  _displayName: Finger Spreading
  _description: "Spread all fingers wide apart on both hands simultaneously, achieving
    at least 35\xB0 between each adjacent pair. Hold the spread position for 2 seconds.
    This exercise improves finger independence and bilateral symmetry."
  _techniqueTips: "- Extend both hands in front of you, palms forward\n- Spread fingers
    as wide as possible\n- Keep both hands symmetrical for a higher score\n- Hold
    the position steady \u2014 don't bounce"
